dct_title_s: Netherlands, North Sea, Texelstroom and Den Helder roads (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Imagery. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From a Netherlands chart of 1997." Not distributed to depository libraries. "Copyright 1998 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." Place names in Dutch with glossary in English. "Soundings in meters." Inset: Den Helder. Scale [ca. 1:15,000]. Includes tidal currents and information. Map no.37238
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
